beer.beer_description:
Chinook / Simcoe / Citra

Some of our favourite OG hops in a Double Hazy IPA. What's not to love!

Pine, citrus and juicy tropical notes make this one of our favourite DIPA's to date.

items.badge_description: Thanks for staying at home, and checking in with Untappd! It allows us to stay connected to a community of beer lovers, just like you, even if we can't be in the same physical location. From our home to yours, cheers and stay safe!

Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 265 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%.  Try 5 more for Level 54!
We believe in IPA and you should too. You certainly have a taste for the hops! That's 145 different IPAs. Try 5 more for Level 30! Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast

items.badge_description: When a single isn’t enough, make it a double. Doubling the hops and malts in a recipe results in a higher ABV and can pack quite a boozey punch. That's 60 different beers with the style that contains Imperial / Double in its style name. Try 5 more for Level 13!

You may not be able to see through the haze, but that juicy, hoppy goodness goes down smooth. What started as a trend is here to stay. That's 85 different beers with the style of IPA - New England / Hazy, Pale Ale - New England / Hazy, IPA - Milkshake, or Pale Ale - Milkshake. Try 5 more for Level 18!
